title: Mother's Market and Kitchen - Santa Ana
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, International, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Health food store and vegetarian kitchen/deli/juice bar. A section of the market is dedicated to the deli and food bars where all food is vegetarian and vegan except for tuna. Hot foods bar, salad bar, juice bar, burritos and tacos bar, olive bar, extensive deli. Vegetarian, vegan, and raw food.
